//practices....

(1) add column in a table by the use of alter command....

(2) changing data type of column in a table by the use of alter command....

(3) change column name in a table by the use of alter command....

(4) adding constraints to a column in a table by the use of alter command....

(5) changing column position in a table by the use of alter command....

(6) delete column in a table by the use of alter command....

(7) Rename tables by the use of alter command....


//methods.....

(1) for add column method....

alter table table_name
add column_name datatype;

(2) modify column....

alter table table_name
modify column_name datatype;

(3) delete column...

alter table table_name
delete column_name datatype;

(4) Rename column....

alter table table_name
change column_name new_name datatype;

(5) rename table....

alter table table_name
rename new_table_name;


